claim.claim-text:
1. An integrated probe, comprising: 
a BGA socket; 
a PGA header comprising a plurality of nail head pins and a pin carrier, said PGA header being soldered to said BGA socket; 
a flexible circuit assembly inserted onto said PGA header; and 
a plurality of solder preforms inserted over said plurality of nail head pins, said preforms having been reflowed.

7. A system for probing bus trace signals from a processor, said system comprising: 
a BGA ZIF socket; 
a PGA header comprising a plurality of nail head pins and a pin carrier, said PGA header being soldered to said BGA socket; 
a flexible circuit assembly inserted onto said PGA header, said flexible circuit having a pair of matched impedance connectors soldered thereto; and 
a plurality of solder preforms inserted over said plurality of nail head pins, said preforms having been reflowed; 
wherein a processor is insertable into said BGA ZIF socket, said system is insertable into a motherboard ZIF socket and processor bus trace signals are capturable from said matched impedance connectors
